Config:
MARKETPLACE_ENABLED=true
MARKETPLACE_INSTALL_ENABLED=true
MARKETPLACE_REVIEW_REQUIRED=true
PLUGIN_RUNTIME_MODE=sandbox
PLUGIN_ALLOW_EXTERNAL_NETWORK=false
PLUGIN_ALLOW_SECRET_ACCESS=false

PluginStatus:
draft, review, approved, rejected, deprecated, disabled

PluginInstallStatus:
installed, enabled, disabled, failed, removed

PluginManifest fields:
id, name, slug, version, description, author, category, status,
required_features, required_permissions, config_schema, default_config,
entrypoint, safety_level, metadata, created_at, updated_at

PluginInstallation fields:
id, organization_id, workspace_id, plugin_id, version, status,
config, enabled, installed_by, installed_at, updated_at

PluginActionResult fields:
plugin_id, action, ok, message, output, dry_run, timestamp

Built-in plugins:
1. zdash-risk-summary
   category: risk
   action: summarize latest risk state

2. zdash-backtest-reporter
   category: backtesting
   action: generate markdown report

3. zdash-content-calendar
   category: content
   action: summarize scheduled content

4. zdash-scheduler-health
   category: automation
   action: summarize scheduler job health

Plugin safety:
- No external network by default.
- No secret access by default.
- No live trading actions.
- No real IoT actions.
- No real social posting.
- Plugins can only call allowed internal services.
- Plugins must be tenant-scoped.
- Plugin install requires marketplace entitlement.
- Plugin safety checker runs before action execution.

Service methods:
- list_plugins()
- get_plugin(plugin_id)
- install_plugin(plugin_id, workspace_id, config)
- enable_plugin(installation_id)
- disable_plugin(installation_id)
- uninstall_plugin(installation_id)
- run_plugin_action(installation_id, action, payload)

Marketplace API:
GET    /api/marketplace/plugins
GET    /api/marketplace/plugins/{plugin_id}
GET    /api/marketplace/installations
POST   /api/marketplace/install
POST   /api/marketplace/installations/{installation_id}/enable
POST   /api/marketplace/installations/{installation_id}/disable
DELETE /api/marketplace/installations/{installation_id}
POST   /api/marketplace/installations/{installation_id}/run

Rules:
- Auth required.
- Tenant scoped.
- Plugin install requires entitlement and quota.
- Plugin run audited.
- Standard response shape.
- Error codes:
  PLUGIN_NOT_FOUND
  PLUGIN_NOT_APPROVED
  PLUGIN_SAFETY_BLOCKED
  FEATURE_NOT_ENTITLED
  QUOTA_EXCEEDED
  TENANT_ACCESS_DENIED

Events:
marketplace.plugin.listed
marketplace.plugin.installed
marketplace.plugin.enabled
marketplace.plugin.disabled
marketplace.plugin.uninstalled
marketplace.plugin.action.started
marketplace.plugin.action.completed
marketplace.plugin.action.blocked
marketplace.plugin.action.failed

